data.description: Introducing an exquisite single family home for sale at 1115 Corkscrew Way! This stunning property boasts 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, providing ample space for your family to grow and thrive. Situated on a generous lot size, this residence offers a spacious backyard perfect for entertaining or simply enjoying the outdoors.    Step inside this wonderful home and be greeted by the beautifully designed floor plan spanning across 2,413 sq ft. The main level features a spacious living room, a well-appointed kitchen, a comfortable dining area, and a convenient half bathroom. Upstairs, you will find the master suite exuding luxury and tranquility, complete with a spacious en-suite bathroom and ample closet space. Additionally, there are three more generously sized bedrooms with plenty of natural light and another full bathroom.    Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your forever home. Call now to schedule a showing and experience the luxury, comfort, and convenience that awaits you at 1115 Corkscrew Way. Seize the chance to create lasting memories in this remarkable residence in a prime location.
